com.mousebird.maply

Interface RenderControllerInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseController, GlobeController, MapController, RenderController

    public interface RenderControllerInterface
    The Render Controller Interface defines the methods a renderer has to implement. These are all done more or less by the same object behind the scenes, but this presents a coherent interface for both onscreen and offscreen renderers.
